	c++: more YY_NULL
	Caught by maintainer-check-g++.
	* data/glr.c, data/lalr1.cc, data/yacc.c, tests/cxx-type.at,
	* tests/glr-regression.at, tests/push.at:
	When simple to do, avoid expliciting the null ptr.
	Otherwise use YY_NULL.

